Below, on the left side, is a chart for each anonymous block of the Letter Patent. The first row of numbers of each chart shows the total word count for that anonymous block; this includes the text in the anonymous block that are the same across all copies and the text that varies, which were tagged using the TEI's critical apparatus tool. Underneath the word count is the string count for each variance between the copies.

Located in the navigation bar across the top is the legend for the chart, depicting the color associated with each copy of the Letter Patent. There are also two check boxes that toglle on and off two sets of bar graphs. One shows the word count that was found the same way as in the chart while the other shows the sum of all the string lengths found within the chart.
